    "heading": "Reason why you should visit Uttarakhand",
    "content": "A land of myths and mountains, Devbhoomi Uttarakhand, is one of the most beautiful states of India.Snow-capped Himalayan peaks, pentine rivers, revered temples, quaint villages, vibrant culture, and World Heritage Sites, Uttarakhand's sheer natural beauty and diversity beckon travelers from across the world."
